25 person and the preliminary plea of not guilty will become a formal
26 plea of not guilty:
27 (A) twenty (20) days after the completion of the initial
28 hearing; or
29 (B) ten (10) days after the completion of the initial hearing if
30 the person is charged only with one (1) or more
